data.description: First showings on Sunday 2/25/24.  Professional photography coming soon. Beautiful, immaculately maintained home in the Southfork Swim Tennis Community, truly a must see! Located in the sought after Loganville school district, near shopping, restaurants and entertainment. This elegant home features a formal dining room with coffered ceiling off of the impressive foyer. Also on the main floor you will find an inviting family room with plenty of space for family and friends and a lovely fireplace. The kitchen with beautiful tile floor features a unique large square island, stunning dark stained cabinetry and a gas stove. This one is an entertainers dream home. The oversized master suite with tray ceiling, features an enormous closet, and a relaxing sitting area. The master bath is a Haven complete with a tiled shower, separate tub and dual vanities. Upstairs, you will also find three additional large bedrooms with plenty of closet space. Any of these rooms could easily serve as your designated office. Outside you have a darling rocking chair front porch and a backyard oasis with privacy fence and covered patio, perfect for entertaining or just relaxing.
